comment.text: This translation key is used to display the text "Setting up Columns" in a UI component, specifically a checkbox label in a portal settings page, allowing users to toggle the visibility of column settings.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While "إعدادات الأعمدة" is a literal translation, "Setting up Columns" often implies configuring or defining columns, rather than just their settings. A more accurate translation might emphasize the process of configuration.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: تكوين الأعمدة (Takween Al-'amoudat) - Meaning 'Configuring the Columns'

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While "Régler" can mean 'to set up,' it often implies adjusting or fixing something. "Setting up Columns" implies a more initial creation or configuration, which "Régler Colonnes" doesn't fully convey. A better translation might focus on creation or configuration.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternatives like "Configurer les colonnes" (to configure columns) or "Créer les colonnes" (to create the columns).

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "열 설정" while literally meaning 'column settings' doesn't fully capture the nuance of 'Setting up Columns' in the context of JavascriptSdk. It implies a simple setting process, whereas 'Setting up Columns' often refers to initial configuration or design.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider a more nuanced translation like "열 구성" (Column Configuration) or "열 디자인" (Column Design), depending on the specific context of JavascriptSdk.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຖັນ" is a literal translation of "Setting up Columns", it might not be the most natural or accurate translation in context. "Setting up Columns" often refers to configuring or arranging columns in a UI or data structure. A more accurate translation might depend on the specific context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternatives like "ການຈັດຖັນຄໍານຸ່ມ" (arrangement of columns) or "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄໍານຸ່ມ" (configuring columns) depending on the specific context.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "තීරූ පිහිටුවමින්" (thirū pihituwamin) is a literal translation and doesn't fully capture the meaning of 'Setting up Columns'. It implies an ongoing process.  'Setting up Columns' often refers to initial configuration or definition.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A more appropriate translation might be "පillarුවල සැකසීම" (pillarwala säkesima) - meaning 'arranging/configuring pillars/columns', or "පillarුවල නිර්ණය" (pillarwala nirṇaya) - meaning 'defining columns'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While "Постављање Колона" is a literal translation of "Setting up Columns", it doesn't convey the full meaning in a technical context. 'Setting up' implies configuration or initialization, which isn't perfectly captured by 'Постављање'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternatives like "Иницијализација Колона" (Initialization of Columns) or "Конфигурисање Колона" (Configuring Columns) depending on the precise meaning intended.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Sütunlar Ayarlanıyor" while literally meaning "Columns are being adjusted" doesn't fully capture the meaning of "Setting up Columns". It implies an ongoing process rather than the initial configuration or setup.
